foreign language)

542
00:21:57,441 --> 00:21:59,651
‐ [Narrator] They say that
man cannot live on bread alone

543
00:21:59,777 --> 00:22:01,067
But Akito may have to

544
00:22:01,153 --> 00:22:02,703
if he wants to keep
his stomach in tact.

545
00:22:02,822 --> 00:22:05,322
In the old days, men were
men and women were women.

546
00:22:05,449 --> 00:22:07,579
But all this equality
of the sexes stuff

547
00:22:07,660 --> 00:22:08,910
has really screwed things up.

548
00:22:08,994 --> 00:22:11,544
Fortunately, there’s
plenty of the old Tabasco.

549
00:22:11,664 --> 00:22:12,624
As we venture onto the meat

550
00:22:12,706 --> 00:22:14,616
for our first swimsuit episode.

551
00:22:14,708 --> 00:22:17,338
But our young hero may not
live long enough to enjoy it

