00:22:17,461 --> 00:22:19,921
when yet another mysterious
lady enters his life.

553
00:22:20,005 --> 00:22:21,545
What is it with this guy?

554
00:22:21,674 --> 00:22:24,554
It’s the next episode of
Martian Successor Nadesico,

555
00:22:24,677 --> 00:22:25,007
the Dangers of Femininity.

